OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778508673
OL,3,CMoss Side stabbing victim named as
OL,4,Cmusician and dad-of-three
OL,6,FA man who was stabbed to death in
OL,7,FManchester on Friday has been named
OL,8,Flocally as father-of-three Adrian
OL,9,FBrown, known as Dre.
OL,11,FMr Brown, who was aged in his 30s, was
OL,12,Fknown in the local area as a musician,
OL,13,Fand was stabbed on Raby Street at
OL,14,Faround 11am on Friday.
OL,16,FHe was taken to hospital but died a
OL,17,Fshort time later.JDetectives have
OL,18,Fdescribed it as a 'targeted' attack
OL,19,Fand a 'shocking act of violence'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
