OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778508673
OL,3,CMoss Side stabbing victim named as
OL,4,Cmusician and dad-of-three
OL,6,FOne a man aged 18 has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder. He remains in
OL,8,Fpolice custody.
OL,10,FTributes have been paid to Mr Brown on
OL,11,Fsocial media.
OL,13,FOne friend said: "RIP, Dre. You will
OL,14,Fbe sadly missed. Gone far too soon.
OL,15,FYou were such a kind soul and amazing
OL,16,Ffather."
OL,18,FAnother described him as a 'good kid'.
OL,19,FA pal wrote: "Rest in peace, Dre".
OL,20,FNatalie Brownlie posted: "RIP Dre."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
