PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778508673
OL,3,CMoss Side stabbing victim named as
OL,4,Cmusician and dad-of-three
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Toby Facey
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a shocking act of
OL,8,Fviolence, and our thoughts remain with
OL,9,Fthe victim and his family at this
OL,10,Fincredibly difficult time. They
OL,11,Fcontinue to be supported by our
OL,12,Fspecialist officers.
OL,14,F"I would like to reassure the
OL,15,Fcommunity that we believe this was a
OL,16,Ftargeted attack and poses no wider
OL,17,Frisk to the public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
